          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MISC CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Better Flying -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">While playing press Circle, R1, R2, Right, Square, L1, L2, Left</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Better Swimming -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">While playing press Square, Square, Triangle, Triangle, X, X, Circle, Circle</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Increase Items -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">At the world map menu press Square + Select</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Level Select -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">At the world map screen press Circle, X, Triangle, Square, Right, Down, Up, Left on controller 2</font>&nbsp;
			<br>&nbsp; Vulture Mode (press X to fly higher and further) -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">During gameplay press Circle, R1, R2, Square, Right, L1, L2, Left</font>&nbsp;<br><br>
	 </tr>
